      <title>俄罗斯认为阿萨德输掉了战争，并迫使他逃离叙利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/russia-pushed-assad-to-flee-syria-after-concluding-he-d-lost-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着叙利亚反对派武装迅速向首都大马士革推进，总统巴沙尔·阿萨德的军队逐渐溃败，他的命运掌握在俄罗斯手中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/russia-pushed-assad-to-flee-syria-after-concluding-he-d-lost-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称日本央行认为等待下次加息成本不高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-cost-to-waiting-for-next-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，日本央行官员认为，等待加息成本不大，而且仍愿意根据数据和市场发展情况在下周加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-cost-to-waiting-for-next-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:11:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国推出减债措施以偿还 260 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/thailand-unveils-debt-relief-measures-to-cover-26-billion-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国出台了一系列新的债务减免措施，为数百万难以偿还贷款的零售借款人和小企业提供援助，这是泰国当局为解决东南亚最高家庭债务水平而采取的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/thailand-unveils-debt-relief-measures-to-cover-26-billion-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约考虑成员国的新武器、装备目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nato-weighs-new-weapons-equipment-targets-for-member-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，北约计划对成员国需要生产多少坦克、飞机和其他武器系统设定新的具体目标，这可能需要将北约的国防开支目标提高到国内生产总值的 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nato-weighs-new-weapons-equipment-targets-for-member-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰财政部长称降低利率将有助于经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/domanski-says-lower-polish-interest-rates-would-be-supportive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰财政部长安杰伊·多曼斯基表示，较低的利率将有利于投资，并补充说与央行存在沟通问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/domanski-says-lower-polish-interest-rates-would-be-supportive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾总统杜特尔特怀疑她能否获得支持以对抗弹劾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特周三表示怀疑她能否获得足够的立法者支持来对抗针对她的弹劾投诉，并称这一过程是一项“政治活动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨请求信任投票，引发提前选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨计划于周三向下议院提交一份请愿书，要求下周一进行信任投票，以引发 2 月底的提前选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚政权垮台后俄罗斯非洲战略面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syria-russia-s-africa-strategy-hanging-by-a-thread-after-regime-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚巴沙尔·阿萨德政权的迅速垮台对俄罗斯在叙利亚的一个重要空军基地构成威胁，莫斯科一直依赖该基地向整个非洲施加影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syria-russia-s-africa-strategy-hanging-by-a-thread-after-regime-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平为应对美国贸易战准备好筹码</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/xi-readies-bargaining-chips-for-us-trade-war-after-biden-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果唐纳德·特朗普兑现其威胁，用关税惩罚世界第二大经济体，中国将展示其准备使用的一系列新工具，以便在与美国爆发贸易战时抢占先机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/xi-readies-bargaining-chips-for-us-trade-war-after-biden-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融家尹永康寻求在调查升级之际继续抗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管韩国总统尹锡烈的戒严宣言调查正在深入，且其所属党派的更多成员表示将支持弹劾，但他似乎决心继续战斗，而不是提前下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
